headline: Growth in AUM Balance Likely to Aid Ameriprise's Q4 Earnings
summary: Ameriprise is set to report Q4 and 2025 results Jan. 29, with higher AUM and revenues expected to lift earnings year over year.

headline: Blackstone Set to Report Q4 Earnings: What's in the Cards?
summary: BX is set to report Q4 and 2025 results on Jan. 29 before the bell, with revenues and earnings expected to fall year over year.
